<ab facs="#facs_104_r2l32">So <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır Jm <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſeıne<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheınbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt <expan>ſeıne<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt <expan>freẅntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab>
